translated: Lewerth, Harald Axel Vilhelm, lawyer, Gothenburg, born on February 17, 1894 in Vänersborg to mining engineer Wilhelm L. and Hilma Schlyter. Married in 1927 to Märtha Uhlin. Children: Lars Anders, born in 1934. Completed secondary studies at Norra Latin in Stockholm in 1912, law degree in Stockholm in 1918. Co-owner of the law firm Drakenberg & von Sneidern in Gothenburg since 1929. Board member of several companies and organizations. Member of the Swedish Bar Association since 1921. Hobbies include horse racing and gardening.
